
ShoppingAdapter -> click item  -> sendBroadcast to ShoppingActivity -> get list item of media -> pass to PlayerService and play

*** Chú ý khi gắn corechat:
- MainActivity lưu tạm danh sách follower vào ChatApplication
- Khi tạo nhóm chat: load danh sách tạm này trước trong main,
- search thì dùng api theo Server_Api goi o main, goi qua lai corechat theo eventbus
    (MH01_MainActivity nhan: EventSearchContactChat_Request, SearchUserChatFromRestApiActivity: EventSearchContactChat_Receive)
- app theme phai mo rong tu material :
 <style name="AppTheme" parent="Theme.MaterialComponents.Light.DarkActionBar">